{"tid":2055816,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"林鄭月娥：一國兩制的「初心」從來沒有變","createTime":"2020-06-08T08:42:56.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-08T11:26:34.000Z","uid":212626,"like":4,"dislike":201,"uniUserReply":89,"replies":[{"pid":"e5c9a50773debc647480db374093b1b2e53d694b","tid":2055816,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-06-08T08:42:57.000Z","msg":"【Now新聞台】行政長官林鄭月娥在基本法頒布三十周年網上研討會致詞，重申全國人大通過決定制訂港區國安法，是合情合理合法合憲，又指就國家安全立法後，香港可在疫情後重新出發。<br />\n<br />\n她又指，港區國安法只針對懲治極少數危害國家安全的人，保障絕大多數奉公守法的人，應得到廣大支持，呼籲公眾思考及理解立法的重要性及必要性，踴躍提出立法意見。<br />\n<br />\n林鄭月娥又指，一國兩制的「初心」，是要維護國家領土完整及保持香港繁榮穩定下，維持港人生活方式，「初心」從來沒有變，訂立國安法可以完善一國兩制制度。<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=393704\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D393704&d=jILigwfPQQ17AL812Qo3KaarsW1wokO1n9cqNe5yO8o%3D&h=453f159d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D393704&h=4741f012\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=393704</a>"},{"pid":"2f6141ca18e3580180f2ba37cec9c67e909ac80e","tid":2055816,"uid":103230,"like":76,"dislike":0,"score":76,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-08T08:43:47.000Z","msg":"初心咪就係呃鳩香港人同全世界<br />\n信你一國兩制<br />\n實際一国一制"},{"pid":"8d76b12fe1199de153509a168a1571383f15510f","tid":2055816,"uid":19552,"like":39,"dislike":0,"score":39,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-06-08T08:44:19.000Z","msg":"陳同佳又係初心"},{"pid":"95c9848cb8e2020060706a6a51de541442883007","tid":2055816,"uid":21470,"like":5,"dislike":5,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-08T08:44:44.000Z","msg":"張曉明：香港主要問題是政治問題 反對派欲奪權變天<br />\n08.06.2020 16:12<br />\n<br />\n港澳辦副主任張曉明表示，香港的主要問題不是經濟、住房、就業民生、年輕人向上流動問題，而是政治問題。他指，反對派和背後的外部勢力，企圖把香港變成獨立或半獨立的政治實體，外部勢力反共反華的橋頭堡，牽制中國發展的棋子，這個就是影響一國兩制全面準確實施，及香港長期繁榮穩定的主要矛盾。<br />\n<br />\n張曉明在特區政府舉辦的基本法頒布30周年網上研討會上指，香港的治權和人心問題比較突出，<span style=\"color: gold;\">需要二次回歸</span>，他提出一系列問題，包括香港社會高度政治化、國安不設防、國民教育難以推行、充斥媒體對國家的各種負面報道、荒誕的試題、大灣區建設受到抵制等，認為反對派是要在香港奪權變天。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=1303357&amp;csid=261_341\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2FPage%2FZH-TW%2Fnewsdetail.aspx%3FItemId%3D1303357%26csid%3D261_341&d=jILigwfPQQ17AL812Qo3KaarsW1wokO1n9cqNe5yO8o%3D&h=eb3edbac\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=1303357&amp;csid=261_341</a>"},{"pid":"dda605c1049a3653badba357a4f124d45add9a1b","tid":2055816,"uid":8880,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-08T08:44:44.000Z","msg":"大魔頭 見到就憎"},{"pid":"a19ecf63c5a6a99d7d2c3b4d1db81867568d08c8","tid":2055816,"uid":177590,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-08T08:45:03.000Z","msg":"是但啦<br />\n自己同鬼佬講啦"},{"pid":"e3ef261c1e302534a4b54609e528e54611347739","tid":2055816,"uid":12599,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-08T08:45:11.000Z","msg":"初心就係殖民香港<br />\n<br />\n只係而家大話俾人踢爆咗only"},{"pid":"6f6ce8dab73b527c5aac3863fed5e051ac5b23c9","tid":2055816,"uid":173179,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-08T08:45:15.000Z","msg":"冇改變<br />\n係唔小心踩到油門姐"},{"pid":"6e65dbf1cd59ec0e33f4747e226272494583cde9","tid":2055816,"uid":83713,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-08T08:45:23.000Z","msg":"初心咪就係要靠香港cap水呃全世界發大財囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"508a4799e8a4a2879c45b47e59fbbc195a925015","tid":2055816,"uid":171849,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-08T08:45:32.000Z","msg":"網上研討會<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n基本法30周年慶典要online搞<br />\n仲要今日朝早先公佈消息<br />\n怕人怕到咁<br />\n柒到冇人有<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img s